WEBVTT

01:43.080 --> 01:45.000
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL
HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

01:51.440 --> 01:54.680
Okay, then our framework is settled.

01:54.760 --> 01:56.920
Afterwards, we'll quickly address

01:57.000 --> 01:58.560
the issue of upgrading the visuals.

01:58.640 --> 01:59.480
Sure.

01:59.560 --> 02:02.440
I'll also update the program schedule

02:02.520 --> 02:04.240
and inform other colleagues.

02:05.080 --> 02:06.240
Thank you for your hard work.

02:06.920 --> 02:07.760
Not at all.

02:09.639 --> 02:12.280
By the way, I've talked
to the building security department

02:12.360 --> 02:13.840
about strengthening the security here.

02:13.920 --> 02:16.200
If Jiang Ying comes again,

02:16.280 --> 02:17.520
they'll notify you in advance.

02:18.400 --> 02:19.720
Sorry for troubling you.

02:19.800 --> 02:21.120
It's no trouble.

02:24.720 --> 02:25.920
I just don't get it.

02:26.400 --> 02:27.760
It has been so many years.

02:27.840 --> 02:30.960
Why can't she let go of you and herself

02:31.040 --> 02:32.600
so everyone can live in peace?

02:35.440 --> 02:37.640
But it was fortunate this time

02:38.160 --> 02:41.080
that she didn't see your relative's child.

02:41.840 --> 02:44.480
Otherwise, who knows
what she would have done?

02:47.520 --> 02:49.040
Don't dwell on it.

02:49.120 --> 02:51.400
Focus on living and working.

02:52.280 --> 02:53.200
I know.

02:54.400 --> 02:55.640
I'll get back to work then.

02:55.720 --> 02:56.880
Go ahead.

03:09.840 --> 03:11.880
How late did you stay up studying?

03:12.360 --> 03:13.920
DON'T COME

03:14.000 --> 03:15.240
It's almost 2:00 a.m.

03:15.320 --> 03:16.680
It's so late.

03:16.760 --> 03:18.600
How was your revision
of the technical overview?

03:18.680 --> 03:20.920
- I'm almost done.
- Don't come straight to my office

03:21.000 --> 03:22.320
or my place anymore.

03:22.880 --> 03:25.080
If you do, let me know beforehand, okay?

03:27.120 --> 03:28.360
Can you lend me your notes?

03:28.440 --> 03:29.880
I need to cram for this subject too.

03:29.960 --> 03:30.840
Okay.

03:30.920 --> 03:32.880
LALALA

03:35.280 --> 03:37.760
Why is this question so hard?

03:37.840 --> 03:39.920
If you can't solve it, let me take a look.

03:43.800 --> 03:46.360
No, I must solve it myself.

03:49.280 --> 03:51.520
I need to eat something first
to replenish my energy.

03:56.040 --> 03:59.120
Is he really not planning to call
and explain it to me?

04:02.800 --> 04:03.880
Sangsang,

04:03.960 --> 04:05.040
do you want some of this?

04:14.080 --> 04:15.480
It's better than yesterday.

04:15.560 --> 04:16.800
Right?

04:17.399 --> 04:18.680
And over here,

04:18.760 --> 04:20.920
it will be better if you test it again

04:21.000 --> 04:22.480
based on the path below.

04:24.040 --> 04:25.000
Again?

04:25.840 --> 04:26.840
Do you want to slack off?

04:28.160 --> 04:29.040
Okay, all right.

04:35.640 --> 04:37.760
But it was fortunate this time

04:38.320 --> 04:41.200
that she didn't see your relative's child.

04:41.840 --> 04:44.360
Otherwise, who knows
what she would have done?

04:58.120 --> 04:59.440
When are your exams?

04:59.520 --> 05:01.560
Have you bought your plane ticket home
for the school break?

05:01.640 --> 05:02.480
BROTHER NO. 2

05:02.560 --> 05:04.040
SANG ZHI

05:04.120 --> 05:05.280
Next week.

05:05.360 --> 05:07.400
I bought a ticket for the 19th.

05:10.440 --> 05:11.480
Okay.

05:16.760 --> 05:17.680
"Okay."

05:20.800 --> 05:25.280
FLIGHT ON THE 19TH

05:25.360 --> 05:30.360
FLIGHT ON THE 19TH

05:38.880 --> 05:42.520
FLIGHT ON THE 19TH

06:01.560 --> 06:02.560
BROTHER NO. 2

06:02.640 --> 06:04.800
When will you be free after your exams?

06:05.440 --> 06:06.560
Let's have a meal together.

06:24.760 --> 06:25.600
SANG ZHI

06:25.680 --> 06:26.680
I might not have time.

06:31.240 --> 06:33.160
She might go out with her friends.

06:33.920 --> 06:34.880
Forget it.

06:49.800 --> 06:50.720
BROTHER NO. 2

06:50.800 --> 06:51.840
Okay.

06:51.920 --> 06:53.800
BROTHER NO.2

07:30.400 --> 07:31.520
I can't focus at all!

07:32.840 --> 07:33.880
What's wrong?

07:33.960 --> 07:35.720
If I fail my classes this time,

07:35.800 --> 07:37.080
it will be all his fault!

07:38.360 --> 07:40.240
WEAK CHEN

07:40.320 --> 07:41.480
Did you fight with Chen Qiang?

07:41.560 --> 07:42.440
How is he capable?

07:42.520 --> 07:44.040
He's only capable of annoying me.

07:44.120 --> 07:45.880
If you ask me, he's extremely weak!

07:45.960 --> 07:46.960
Weak Chen!

07:50.560 --> 07:51.920
Stop looking at it.

07:57.560 --> 08:00.040
JANUARY 10TH, WEDNESDAY

08:06.160 --> 08:07.080
I've had it.

08:08.360 --> 08:10.360
It's imperative for me
to change my mood immediately!

08:11.120 --> 08:12.920
Ning Wei, what do you have in mind?

08:15.920 --> 08:17.960
I've had enough of the bitterness of love.

08:18.040 --> 08:18.960
Only drinking

08:19.040 --> 08:20.520
can relieve it.

08:23.360 --> 08:24.560
After our exams are over,

08:24.640 --> 08:25.520
let's go and have fun.

08:26.480 --> 08:28.120
Why don't we go today?

08:30.400 --> 08:31.280
But I thought

08:31.760 --> 08:34.360
your mom will call you in a little while.

08:35.720 --> 08:37.240
We have exams tomorrow.

08:37.720 --> 08:38.600
That's right.

08:39.679 --> 08:42.360
Then can we go after our exams?

08:42.440 --> 08:44.120
- Sure, okay.
- I agree.

08:44.840 --> 08:46.480
Okay, everyone is on board.

08:46.560 --> 08:48.040
I'll text Jiang Ming right now

08:48.120 --> 08:50.480
and officially tell Weak Chen
not to show up!

08:50.560 --> 08:51.520
Yes, very impressive.

08:51.600 --> 08:56.920
Baby, answer the phone.

08:57.000 --> 08:57.840
Baby…

08:58.920 --> 08:59.840
What do you want?

09:09.120 --> 09:10.200
What?

09:10.280 --> 09:11.120
No.

09:11.200 --> 09:12.560
You're so annoying.

09:15.600 --> 09:16.960
Okay, fine.

09:17.040 --> 09:18.400
I'll be down there right away.

09:20.360 --> 09:21.200
Bye.

09:27.520 --> 09:29.400
Ladies, I'll be…

09:29.480 --> 09:30.600
Just go.

09:32.240 --> 09:33.240
I can't stand you.

09:35.320 --> 09:36.360
Weiwei.

09:37.040 --> 09:38.200
Be safe.

09:38.280 --> 09:39.280
- Okay.
- Close the door.

09:39.360 --> 09:40.600
- I know.
- I meant Chen Qiang.

09:40.680 --> 09:41.800
What?

09:44.520 --> 09:45.640
I'm going to shower.

09:45.720 --> 09:46.560
Okay.

09:54.040 --> 09:54.880
Sangsang.

09:57.880 --> 10:01.400
Do you have something on your mind lately?

10:03.360 --> 10:05.920
You may not show it,

10:06.400 --> 10:08.160
but I could sense

10:08.240 --> 10:10.360
that you've been down lately.

10:11.400 --> 10:12.560
I think

10:12.640 --> 10:13.840
it started from the day

10:13.920 --> 10:15.440
you delivered the peephole camera.

10:16.320 --> 10:17.480
Could it be

10:17.560 --> 10:19.640
that the relative
to whom you gave the peephole camera

10:19.720 --> 10:21.800
is your crush?

10:26.920 --> 10:27.840
Well,

10:29.200 --> 10:31.400
something did happen that day.

10:33.440 --> 10:35.560
But it's not really anything serious.

10:36.760 --> 10:38.760
Maybe I'm overthinking it.

10:42.400 --> 10:44.520
Do you two still keep in touch?

10:52.320 --> 10:53.400
We do.

10:53.960 --> 10:54.880
But…

10:59.440 --> 11:01.960
I think you're really nice to him.

11:02.040 --> 11:03.840
But if he doesn't treat you well,

11:04.880 --> 11:06.120
you should move on.

11:07.160 --> 11:08.440
He treats me well too.

11:09.640 --> 11:10.760
It's just that…

11:19.080 --> 11:21.040
Wangwang, I'm fine.

11:21.120 --> 11:22.120
Don't worry about me.

11:22.840 --> 11:23.840
I mean it.

11:49.000 --> 11:51.560
CHAPTER 12, COURAGE

11:51.640 --> 11:53.400
IF I COULD

11:54.640 --> 11:55.720
- Five.
- Be more accurate.

11:55.800 --> 11:57.280
- Six.
- Demonstrate it.

11:57.360 --> 11:58.360
It's six.

11:58.920 --> 12:00.160
Sexy six.

12:02.080 --> 12:03.320
Which one are you drinking?

12:05.240 --> 12:06.120
I don't get it at all.

12:06.600 --> 12:08.120
Don't ruin my rhythm.

12:09.400 --> 12:10.560
How did your exams go?

12:11.920 --> 12:13.240
Not too bad.

12:13.800 --> 12:15.240
Are you going home tomorrow?

12:15.320 --> 12:16.800
I'm free tomorrow. I can see you off.

12:17.760 --> 12:18.880
Don't you have training?

12:19.560 --> 12:20.600
You don't have to.

12:20.680 --> 12:22.560
Go to your training. I can manage.

12:24.840 --> 12:25.760
Okay.

12:26.360 --> 12:27.560
Does your drink taste good?

12:27.640 --> 12:28.720
Try it.

12:30.560 --> 12:31.880
This one has a stronger kick.

12:32.920 --> 12:34.240
If I drink it,

12:34.320 --> 12:35.280
I get drunk quickly.

12:35.360 --> 12:36.560
- It's true.
- You're weak.

12:36.640 --> 12:37.720
Try a little.

12:38.320 --> 12:39.680
Not too much. You don't drink.

12:39.760 --> 12:40.920
Are you feeling dizzy?

12:45.400 --> 12:46.760
Not bad.

12:47.240 --> 12:48.400
Impressive.

12:48.480 --> 12:49.360
Okay, where were we?

12:49.440 --> 12:50.720
- It's my turn.
- Your turn.

12:50.800 --> 12:51.720
- Five.
- Five.

12:51.800 --> 12:53.440
- Six.
- I mean five.

12:53.520 --> 12:55.080
- Five.
- Six.

12:56.040 --> 12:57.680
Do you want to try to add

12:57.760 --> 12:59.320
that screen space ambient occlusion?

13:00.360 --> 13:02.800
It can add more depth
to the entire environment.

13:03.880 --> 13:05.120
You're right. I'll try that.

13:05.200 --> 13:06.040
Go and try it.

13:06.120 --> 13:07.480
Okay. Thank you, Jiaxu.

13:18.480 --> 13:19.440
DUAN JIAXU

13:19.520 --> 13:20.640
You're going home tomorrow.

13:20.720 --> 13:22.000
Have you packed your luggage?

13:29.760 --> 13:30.800
Thank you, everyone.

13:32.560 --> 13:33.680
That was good.

13:42.200 --> 13:43.160
Where is he going?

13:43.240 --> 13:44.520
Don't tell me he's going to sing.

13:47.680 --> 13:48.880
I'll send you to the airport.

13:55.920 --> 13:57.160
Sorry, everyone,

13:57.240 --> 13:58.680
for taking some of your time.

13:59.840 --> 14:03.200
I want to dedicate a song to…

14:07.600 --> 14:08.760
To my friends.

14:10.040 --> 14:10.920
- Okay!
- Good!

14:22.880 --> 14:26.160
How do I describe your face?

14:27.240 --> 14:29.680
Cute with a hint of shyness

14:30.160 --> 14:31.520
I really want to have

14:32.320 --> 14:35.920
A little bit of something with you

14:37.240 --> 14:40.000
Can I call you this?

14:40.920 --> 14:43.720
Standing like a fool outside your place

14:44.320 --> 14:46.240
Dialing the phone

14:46.320 --> 14:49.520
Looking at the cooling egg tart

14:50.160 --> 14:52.320
I didn't expect Jiang Ming

14:52.400 --> 14:53.720
to be good at singing.

14:54.440 --> 14:55.680
Besides,

14:55.760 --> 14:57.440
- look…
- Just to get a smile

14:57.520 --> 14:59.840
Jiang Ming looks handsome
like this, right?

14:59.920 --> 15:01.600
- Right?
- Nonsense.

15:01.680 --> 15:04.040
Why don't we be together?

15:04.120 --> 15:06.440
Of course, he's not as handsome as you.

15:06.520 --> 15:09.520
Since the day I met you

15:09.600 --> 15:11.880
I've liked you

15:13.520 --> 15:14.520
Meeting…

15:14.600 --> 15:15.960
I'm going to the restroom.

15:16.040 --> 15:17.360
Do you want me to go with you?

15:17.440 --> 15:19.760
They're all about you

15:19.840 --> 15:20.800
She drank too much.

15:20.880 --> 15:24.320
Watching the ebb and flow
of the ocean's surface

15:24.400 --> 15:27.720
Reminds me of you

15:27.800 --> 15:30.680
Carefully

15:31.520 --> 15:33.760
I store you in my mind

15:33.840 --> 15:38.560
A repeating melody

15:38.640 --> 15:39.800
Hello?

15:40.520 --> 15:41.880
Why didn't you reply to my message?

15:45.280 --> 15:46.200
Hello?

15:53.600 --> 15:54.560
Where are you?

15:55.600 --> 15:57.240
I'm at a bar.

15:58.880 --> 16:00.040
Who are you with?

16:01.240 --> 16:02.320
My friends.

16:04.160 --> 16:05.040
Did you drink?

16:05.520 --> 16:06.360
Just a little.

16:07.120 --> 16:08.200
What's the name of the bar?

16:10.360 --> 16:17.280
- I've liked you since the first day…
- Qinghong Music 2002 Music Bar

16:18.280 --> 16:20.480
Okay. Wait inside.

16:20.560 --> 16:21.440
I'm coming over now.

16:21.520 --> 16:22.720
Why are you coming?

16:24.240 --> 16:25.880
To catch a drunkard.

16:28.960 --> 16:29.920
Hello?

16:30.000 --> 16:32.480
If I could

16:33.440 --> 16:37.640
I would cover your island with stars

16:37.720 --> 16:39.680
You won't let me go and see you.

16:39.760 --> 16:41.160
But you want to come and see me.

16:42.920 --> 16:43.920
You're so weird.

16:44.680 --> 16:48.840
Preserve your gentle childishness

16:48.920 --> 16:53.040
And just never wake up

16:54.600 --> 16:55.880
Thank you.

16:59.480 --> 17:00.880
I'm going to go back now.

17:01.440 --> 17:02.640
Are you leaving now?

17:02.720 --> 17:04.800
- How can we let you go like this?
- Are you drunk?

17:04.880 --> 17:05.880
I'm fine.

17:05.960 --> 17:07.200
My brother is picking me up.

17:07.280 --> 17:08.480
Bye, guys.

17:08.560 --> 17:10.079
- Is she going alone?
- I'll go with her.

17:10.160 --> 17:11.800
- Yes, go.
- Go quickly.

17:12.760 --> 17:14.160
She should be fine, right?

17:14.240 --> 17:15.160
She'll be fine.

17:24.920 --> 17:25.760
Be careful.

17:27.480 --> 17:28.319
It's okay.

17:29.200 --> 17:30.480
- I'm fine.
- Watch your step.

17:36.680 --> 17:37.560
Careful.

17:40.640 --> 17:42.040
You don't have to follow me.

17:42.120 --> 17:43.960
You can stay with them.

17:44.040 --> 17:45.160
I didn't drink that much.

17:45.240 --> 17:47.400
I'll wait here for my brother
to pick me up.

17:49.680 --> 17:51.480
Are you cold? You're not wearing much.

17:52.400 --> 17:53.600
I'm not cold!

17:53.680 --> 17:54.600
I'm really not cold.

17:59.120 --> 18:00.000
Sang Zhi.

18:01.480 --> 18:04.080
Actually, I wanted to dedicate that song

18:04.680 --> 18:05.920
to you.

18:08.680 --> 18:09.640
I…

18:11.120 --> 18:12.000
I…

18:14.480 --> 18:15.760
- What's wrong?
- I'm fine.

18:15.840 --> 18:17.160
I'll stay like this for a bit.

18:17.640 --> 18:19.080
I'll help you over to that bench.

18:19.160 --> 18:20.000
No, it's okay.

18:25.240 --> 18:26.600
- This isn't good.
- I'm really okay.

18:26.680 --> 18:28.600
- I'm okay. Don't touch me.
- Let's go over there.

18:35.960 --> 18:36.840
What are you doing?

18:38.400 --> 18:39.600
Jiaxu.

18:42.760 --> 18:43.600
Get up first.

18:45.480 --> 18:47.080
I didn't drink a lot.

18:47.160 --> 18:48.400
I'm fine.

18:50.640 --> 18:52.080
Are you Sang Zhi's brother?

18:52.160 --> 18:53.400
I'm Sang Zhi's schoolmate.

18:53.480 --> 18:54.400
My name is Jiang Ming.

18:55.080 --> 18:56.000
Nice to meet you.

18:56.840 --> 18:57.880
I'm here now.

18:58.600 --> 18:59.760
So thank you.

19:01.760 --> 19:03.040
Okay.

19:03.120 --> 19:04.200
Then I'll go back inside.

19:11.360 --> 19:12.720
Where are we going?

19:13.800 --> 19:15.440
Who said you could drink at a bar?

19:18.760 --> 19:20.120
I'm an adult.

19:20.720 --> 19:22.960
I'm a grown-up. Why can't I visit a bar?

19:24.640 --> 19:26.120
Even so, you can't drink this much.

19:26.200 --> 19:28.160
Why can't I be here when I'm an adult?

19:36.000 --> 19:37.200
Are you angry?

19:41.760 --> 19:42.920
You said so.

19:44.080 --> 19:47.080
You told me that when I grow up,

19:47.160 --> 19:49.680
I can do what I want.

19:50.480 --> 19:53.640
But now, I've grown up.

19:53.720 --> 19:55.200
I'm already an adult.

19:56.160 --> 19:57.440
But there are many things

19:57.520 --> 19:59.000
that I still can't do.

20:01.200 --> 20:02.720
Or maybe I'm afraid to do them.

20:06.880 --> 20:07.720
Where are you going?

20:08.320 --> 20:09.320
Home.

20:15.160 --> 20:16.200
What's the matter?

20:16.680 --> 20:18.000
I feel sick.

20:18.080 --> 20:19.320
I feel like throwing up.

20:21.200 --> 20:22.160
Then go ahead.

20:22.240 --> 20:23.400
You'll feel better afterwards.

20:25.360 --> 20:26.640
I can't.

20:28.600 --> 20:30.040
Let's go sit over there for a bit.

20:30.120 --> 20:30.960
No.

20:31.040 --> 20:32.360
We'll just stay here.

20:35.520 --> 20:36.920
You're squatting in the cold.

20:37.000 --> 20:38.240
Getting a cold will be worse.

20:38.320 --> 20:39.720
I just want to stay here for a bit.

20:39.800 --> 20:41.160
I don't feel well.

20:41.920 --> 20:43.560
I'll carry you there, okay?

20:43.640 --> 20:45.120
- I--
- Be good.

20:45.200 --> 20:46.640
I don't want to move!

20:47.240 --> 20:48.400
Be good.

20:48.480 --> 20:49.360
Get up.

21:35.600 --> 21:36.440
I'm sorry.

21:37.280 --> 21:38.200
I…

21:38.280 --> 21:39.480
Why are you apologizing?

21:39.560 --> 21:40.800
I'm sorry.

21:41.640 --> 21:42.520
It's okay.

21:43.200 --> 21:44.480
It's disgusting.

21:47.800 --> 21:49.200
- What's wrong?
- Don't be mean to me.

21:51.520 --> 21:52.560
Do you want to throw up?

21:54.800 --> 21:56.040
Just do it if you want to.

22:02.920 --> 22:05.000
Don't be mean to me.

22:06.800 --> 22:08.120
I won't.

22:09.160 --> 22:10.960
When have I ever been mean to you?

22:19.840 --> 22:21.160
Can you hold on a little longer?

22:25.520 --> 22:26.440
It's windy here.

22:26.520 --> 22:27.880
It won't be good if you get a cold.

22:29.280 --> 22:30.440
Let's go.

22:30.520 --> 22:31.360
I'll carry you.

22:36.400 --> 22:37.240
What's wrong?

22:37.320 --> 22:38.720
You can't carry me.

22:39.280 --> 22:40.640
Why not?

22:40.720 --> 22:42.440
The doctor said it.

22:42.520 --> 22:44.000
You've had surgery.

22:45.160 --> 22:46.040
Over here.

22:46.600 --> 22:48.440
You can't do any heavy lifting

22:48.520 --> 22:50.240
for three months.

22:50.320 --> 22:52.160
- Over here.
- Three months have passed.

22:54.760 --> 22:55.600
Really?

22:57.800 --> 22:58.640
Then…

23:00.320 --> 23:02.720
Can you carry me?

23:02.800 --> 23:03.640
Sure.

23:05.360 --> 23:06.600
Get up and I'll carry you.

23:13.680 --> 23:14.520
Come on.

23:18.680 --> 23:19.520
Get on.

23:24.440 --> 23:26.200
I must be crazy!

23:28.080 --> 23:29.840
You can't carry me.

23:30.720 --> 23:32.200
Why not?

23:32.280 --> 23:34.080
I weigh over 45 kg.

23:36.520 --> 23:38.440
I weigh over 45 kg.

23:40.120 --> 23:43.280
But the thing is that I'm still flat.

23:43.360 --> 23:45.280
What are you talking about?

23:45.360 --> 23:47.840
I weigh over 45 kg.

23:48.600 --> 23:49.520
Hold on.

23:49.600 --> 23:52.120
It's really flat.

23:53.280 --> 23:54.720
What is flat?

23:55.840 --> 23:57.280
You're laughing.

23:59.160 --> 24:00.400
Do you even have them?

24:02.160 --> 24:03.080
Wait.

24:08.280 --> 24:09.560
I don't.

24:09.640 --> 24:11.040
I don't have them either.

24:11.120 --> 24:12.280
Get up first.

24:12.360 --> 24:13.440
I really don't have any.

24:17.920 --> 24:18.920
But I hope

24:20.080 --> 24:21.880
you won't be too sad about it.

24:23.040 --> 24:24.480
Things like this

24:26.640 --> 24:29.440
are beyond our control.

24:30.760 --> 24:32.240
Okay.

24:32.320 --> 24:33.200
I won't feel sad.

24:33.760 --> 24:34.840
If I'm not sad,

24:34.920 --> 24:36.200
you must not be sad either.

24:36.280 --> 24:37.160
No more crying.

24:38.160 --> 24:39.000
Stop crying.

24:42.480 --> 24:43.360
Now,

24:44.440 --> 24:45.680
can I carry you home?

24:49.640 --> 24:50.520
Be good.

24:50.600 --> 24:51.800
Stop crying.

24:58.600 --> 24:59.800
Get on.

25:05.320 --> 25:06.240
Stay still.

25:12.240 --> 25:13.280
Stop crying, okay?

25:15.520 --> 25:16.440
Then

25:17.360 --> 25:20.440
what if I want to throw up again?

25:21.800 --> 25:23.360
Before you throw up,

25:24.080 --> 25:25.240
give me a heads-up.

25:26.240 --> 25:27.800
I'll try not to sway too much

25:28.720 --> 25:29.960
so you'll feel more comfortable.

25:34.320 --> 25:35.800
Then I'll just do this.

25:37.840 --> 25:39.600
- Okay.
- Then I won't throw up.

25:54.880 --> 25:55.720
Jiaxu.

25:59.600 --> 26:01.080
I have a secret.

26:04.920 --> 26:05.800
A secret

26:08.760 --> 26:10.840
that I've been hiding in my heart.

26:12.800 --> 26:13.880
Do you want to tell me?

26:16.160 --> 26:17.000
Well,

26:18.840 --> 26:19.880
there is

26:22.520 --> 26:23.440
someone

26:25.760 --> 26:27.120
that I really like.

26:30.880 --> 26:31.800
But

26:34.800 --> 26:36.280
he just doesn't like me.

26:43.080 --> 26:43.920
Who is it?

26:47.440 --> 26:49.040
I can't tell you.

26:51.120 --> 26:52.600
Not even me?

26:55.400 --> 26:56.600
Yes.

27:02.240 --> 27:03.920
Zhizhi is sad.

27:08.920 --> 27:10.400
Zhizhi is so sad.

27:14.320 --> 27:15.440
Is that

27:17.040 --> 27:18.440
because of the person you like?

27:24.480 --> 27:26.120
Are you sure you can't tell me who it is?

27:30.680 --> 27:32.040
Then tell me

27:33.720 --> 27:35.040
what kind of person he is.

27:36.360 --> 27:37.480
Does he treat you well?

27:40.200 --> 27:41.480
You can tell me that much, right?

27:46.280 --> 27:47.160
He is…

27:48.200 --> 27:49.080
He…

27:52.840 --> 27:53.760
What?

28:01.360 --> 28:03.240
I don't know how to put it into words.

28:07.360 --> 28:08.440
What do you mean?

28:10.440 --> 28:12.120
He's really nice.

28:14.760 --> 28:16.680
He's also really nice to me.

28:18.600 --> 28:21.640
But he's nice to everyone.

28:25.160 --> 28:27.560
He's nice to everybody.

28:33.440 --> 28:35.160
He's a ladies' man.

28:42.360 --> 28:44.520
So he has made you so heartbroken.

28:48.920 --> 28:50.160
If he's someone like that,

28:53.440 --> 28:54.760
stop liking him.

28:56.120 --> 28:57.000
Can you do that?

29:51.000 --> 29:51.880
Sang Zhi.

30:01.040 --> 30:03.000
So that's the kind of guy you like.

30:11.080 --> 30:13.040
Why don't I become like him?

30:16.320 --> 30:18.240
And I'll be nice to you alone.

30:20.640 --> 30:21.920
That way, our Sang Zhi

30:24.600 --> 30:26.480
probably won't be so sad anymore.

30:33.120 --> 30:34.680
Letting someone else take care of you

30:37.600 --> 30:39.480
doesn't put me at ease at all.

30:46.960 --> 30:48.040
If you don't say anything,

30:48.920 --> 30:50.440
I'll take it as a yes.

30:59.880 --> 31:01.640
My situation has improved.

31:04.360 --> 31:05.520
I've paid all my debts.

31:06.520 --> 31:08.040
I have a pretty great personality.

31:10.920 --> 31:11.960
The only thing is that

31:12.520 --> 31:14.160
I'm a bit older than you.

31:17.600 --> 31:19.240
When I was 21,

31:19.800 --> 31:21.000
you already thought I was old.

31:23.000 --> 31:24.440
Now, rounding up,

31:24.520 --> 31:25.760
you're almost 20.

31:28.720 --> 31:30.440
Sang Zhi is a grown-up now.

32:10.520 --> 32:11.920
What am I doing?

32:48.040 --> 32:48.880
I threw up.

32:50.000 --> 32:51.800
I threw up on Jiaxu.

33:13.600 --> 33:14.520
He…

33:16.520 --> 33:17.560
He said…

33:21.760 --> 33:22.680
Forget it.

33:23.920 --> 33:25.760
What was there to say

33:25.840 --> 33:26.960
to a drunkard like me?

33:44.720 --> 33:45.800
BROTHER NO. 2

33:45.880 --> 33:46.880
Are you up?

33:46.960 --> 33:48.880
I asked your roommate
to wake you up at nine.

33:49.400 --> 33:51.640
All the flights at this time are sold out.

33:51.720 --> 33:52.840
You can't change your flight.

33:52.920 --> 33:54.200
You have to get up

33:54.280 --> 33:55.320
or you won't make it home.

33:56.200 --> 33:57.760
Drink a lot of water after you wake up.

33:58.240 --> 33:59.400
I'll pick you up at ten

33:59.480 --> 34:00.720
and take you to the airport.

34:21.880 --> 34:23.679
- You're up.
- You're finally awake, Sangsang.

34:24.480 --> 34:25.360
Yes.

34:25.440 --> 34:26.639
How do you feel?

34:26.719 --> 34:27.719
- Slowly.
- Watch your head.

34:28.480 --> 34:30.280
Is the guy who brought you back last night

34:30.360 --> 34:33.280
your brother's friend, your crush,

34:33.360 --> 34:34.960
whom you mentioned before?

34:35.040 --> 34:36.000
Is he the one?

34:38.760 --> 34:39.840
You said he is handsome,

34:39.920 --> 34:42.239
but you didn't say he is that handsome!

34:42.320 --> 34:43.320
I told you before.

34:43.400 --> 34:45.360
How was I to know

34:45.440 --> 34:46.679
that he is this good-looking?

34:47.639 --> 34:49.199
Compared to Chen Qiang,

34:49.280 --> 34:50.440
Chen Qiang is truly weak.

34:50.520 --> 34:52.600
He's no match for him. Not even close.

34:52.679 --> 34:54.880
By the way,

34:54.960 --> 34:57.160
when he brought me back here yesterday,

34:57.840 --> 35:00.520
did he

35:01.480 --> 35:02.680
seem upset?

35:02.760 --> 35:03.640
No.

35:03.720 --> 35:04.880
Did he look unhappy?

35:05.520 --> 35:06.760
- No.
- No.

35:06.840 --> 35:08.200
He looked pretty fine to me.

35:08.280 --> 35:09.600
Unhappy?

35:09.680 --> 35:10.600
Wait a minute.

35:11.120 --> 35:12.600
Did you do something?

35:13.280 --> 35:14.520
- Nothing.
- What did you do?

35:14.600 --> 35:15.560
Nothing.

35:15.640 --> 35:17.000
Nothing? I don't believe you.

35:17.080 --> 35:18.440
I didn't do anything.

35:18.520 --> 35:20.840
Anyway, you guys have to watch me.

35:20.920 --> 35:22.440
I must never drink anymore.

35:22.520 --> 35:24.360
If I ever drink, I'm a dog.

35:25.760 --> 35:27.040
- You're serious.
- What did you do?

35:27.120 --> 35:28.360
Did you kiss him?

35:29.240 --> 35:30.840
No, I didn't. I would never.

35:30.920 --> 35:32.680
- Why are you so worked up?
- You must have.

35:32.760 --> 35:34.720
You must have confessed
your feelings to him!

35:34.800 --> 35:35.960
- Am I right?
- Did you confess?

35:36.040 --> 35:37.320
If I did confess,

35:37.400 --> 35:39.120
I probably wouldn't have woken up today.

35:39.200 --> 35:41.000
- Then what did you do?
- What did you do to him?

35:41.080 --> 35:42.320
- Tell us. Come on.
- Nothing!

35:42.400 --> 35:44.040
- I didn't--
- She couldn't have vomited.

35:44.120 --> 35:45.440
- Impossible.
- You didn't, did you?

35:48.840 --> 35:49.840
Did you really throw up?

35:49.920 --> 35:50.840
Did you really

35:51.400 --> 35:52.640
throw up on him?

35:52.720 --> 35:53.560
Well…

35:54.080 --> 35:55.720
I need to pack my things.

35:55.800 --> 35:57.520
I have to pack up my stuff.

35:59.040 --> 36:00.360
So she did throw up.

36:00.440 --> 36:02.520
She threw up on him.

36:02.600 --> 36:05.760
Sangsang, you threw up on your crush!

36:15.920 --> 36:17.720
Why does he insist on seeing me off?

36:18.920 --> 36:20.040
How can I face him

36:21.320 --> 36:22.840
after what happened last night?

36:56.360 --> 36:57.880
Good morning, Jiaxu.

37:00.440 --> 37:01.560
Good morning.

37:04.640 --> 37:06.320
Let me help you with your luggage.

37:14.000 --> 37:14.880
Sang Zhi!

37:15.480 --> 37:16.520
Jiang Ming.

37:17.520 --> 37:19.000
- Good morning.
- Are you okay?

37:19.080 --> 37:20.480
You drank a lot last night.

37:20.560 --> 37:21.600
I'm okay.

37:23.040 --> 37:24.240
Do you need anything from me?

37:26.000 --> 37:27.400
You were drunk last night.

37:27.920 --> 37:29.440
So I don't know

37:29.520 --> 37:31.520
if you still remember what I said.

37:33.760 --> 37:34.600
I'm sorry.

37:34.680 --> 37:36.760
I don't really remember.

37:36.840 --> 37:37.840
I…

37:40.040 --> 37:41.000
Hi there.

37:42.080 --> 37:42.920
You guys can talk.

37:46.720 --> 37:47.960
Sorry, Sang Zhi.

37:48.040 --> 37:49.440
I didn't know your brother was here.

37:50.640 --> 37:51.600
It's okay.

37:52.240 --> 37:53.720
What were you saying just now?

37:56.520 --> 37:59.360
Actually, I wanted to tell you this
on New Year's Eve,

37:59.440 --> 38:01.040
but you didn't come that night.

38:02.720 --> 38:03.840
Last night,

38:05.000 --> 38:06.400
I sang a song at the bar.

38:06.480 --> 38:07.680
- Song?
- It was for you--

38:08.880 --> 38:10.080
Yes.

38:10.160 --> 38:12.360
I played the guitar and sang at the bar.

38:14.040 --> 38:16.560
You even played the guitar and sang.

38:17.320 --> 38:19.040
I prepared the performance for you.

38:19.120 --> 38:20.120
For me?

38:20.680 --> 38:21.800
I had prepared that song

38:22.720 --> 38:23.560
for a long time.

38:24.720 --> 38:25.600
Thank you.

38:29.160 --> 38:30.400
Sang Zhi.

38:33.840 --> 38:34.760
I like you.

38:38.640 --> 38:39.760
I want you to know that.

38:42.920 --> 38:44.240
It's nice

38:44.320 --> 38:46.040
to have people who like you.

38:46.120 --> 38:48.520
You can thank him for liking you

38:48.600 --> 38:50.720
before gently rejecting him.

39:02.200 --> 39:03.680
Thank you for liking me.

39:04.240 --> 39:05.520
I understand.

39:06.480 --> 39:07.400
However…

39:10.880 --> 39:12.200
There is someone else I like.

39:13.200 --> 39:14.320
So

39:14.400 --> 39:15.280
I'm sorry.

39:18.520 --> 39:19.440
It's okay.

39:19.520 --> 39:21.320
There's no need to apologize.

39:22.000 --> 39:23.680
We're still friends

39:24.640 --> 39:25.840
after this, right?

39:27.080 --> 39:27.960
Of course.

39:31.920 --> 39:33.760
Eat this for breakfast on the road.

39:36.160 --> 39:37.000
Okay.

39:38.080 --> 39:38.920
Thank you.

39:39.520 --> 39:41.600
Get in the car. Your brother is waiting.

39:43.000 --> 39:44.320
I'll get going then.

39:44.400 --> 39:45.240
Bye.

40:03.080 --> 40:04.000
Is it delicious?

40:09.920 --> 40:10.880
Then eat more.

40:11.880 --> 40:13.240
I have something to ask you later.

40:24.480 --> 40:26.920
We went to the bar yesterday because…

40:27.880 --> 40:29.840
Because we…

40:35.280 --> 40:37.640
We had made plans to have fun

40:37.720 --> 40:39.040
after the exams.

40:39.640 --> 40:41.440
The bar is also close

40:43.040 --> 40:44.960
to the campus,

40:45.040 --> 40:47.080
so there were mostly students.

40:47.160 --> 40:49.480
It was not dangerous at all.

40:54.840 --> 40:56.120
Also, you know

40:57.280 --> 40:59.880
that I don't usually drink much.

40:59.960 --> 41:01.320
- So--
- Who did you go with?

41:04.360 --> 41:05.280
My roommates.

41:05.840 --> 41:07.360
They were all people I know.

41:07.440 --> 41:08.440
Roommates?

41:08.520 --> 41:10.960
What about the guy
who came out with you yesterday?

41:11.520 --> 41:12.560
The one who is 195 cm tall

41:13.240 --> 41:14.760
and just gave you a hamburger.

41:15.840 --> 41:17.160
Is he also your roommate?

41:17.240 --> 41:20.440
No, that is my roommate's
boyfriend's friend.

41:22.520 --> 41:23.360
Is that him?

41:26.160 --> 41:27.640
What do you mean?

41:28.400 --> 41:29.640
The guy you like.

41:30.200 --> 41:31.360
Is it him?

41:38.240 --> 41:39.160
Is he?

42:11.440 --> 42:12.520
What is this?

42:15.320 --> 42:16.880
The breakfast he just gave me.

42:19.640 --> 42:21.320
Is this a beef burger?

42:21.400 --> 42:23.440
You can't eat this. I'll take it.

42:35.000 --> 42:36.360
I'm sorry, Jiaxu.

42:39.120 --> 42:42.080
I threw up on you yesterday, right?

42:42.160 --> 42:43.640
I didn't dream it, did I?

42:47.280 --> 42:49.720
Are you really that hungry?

42:50.280 --> 42:51.120
No.

42:55.080 --> 42:59.120
Why don't you give me the dirty clothes?

42:59.200 --> 43:01.240
I'll return them to you
after I clean them.

43:02.920 --> 43:04.920
You drank quite a lot last night.

43:06.040 --> 43:07.320
It's okay.

43:07.400 --> 43:09.160
I knew you would have a hangover today,

43:10.040 --> 43:11.000
so have some fruit.

43:11.080 --> 43:13.320
I'll buy you a hot drink at the airport.

43:16.240 --> 43:17.200
Thank you.

43:23.120 --> 43:24.360
Let's go.
